txt.en: Tansy Haresfoot can be found at Sutwarden in the Wildwood.\n\nYou should summon and confront Tansy Haresfoot.
You have defeated Tansy Haresfoot and assisted the Free Peoples of the Wildwood.
A bounty notice asks you to seek out Tansy Haresfoot, a deadly Brigand in Wildwood.

The bounty notice reads:

'She stood atop the hill, and I knew she spied me from afar. Tansy Haresfoot, the deadly assassin, watched me. I was lucky for I was not her target on that day. How long must we live in fear when we harvest the bountiful resources of the Wildwood?

'I offer a reward to any who can rid these woods of Tansy Haresfoot. I never want to see that Brigand on the higher ground in the Wildwood ever again!'
'I could have killed you already. Remember that.'
'You want to bring me in? I wish you luck!'
